---
alwaysApply: true
---

name: workspace-safety
description: Prevent unapproved file deletions or overwrites.
rules:
  - Never delete, remove, or overwrite any user files unless explicitly instructed by the user to do so.
  - Always confirm and require user approval before performing any action that results in file deletion or loss of data.
  - Preserve original files when making modifications by saving changes to a new file, unless otherwise specified.
